    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3131980/extras/8532d6473e6d252c76239a94e5c1b1e9.avif?t=1753943646\" width=616 height=215 /></span><br><br>Explore and progress through 4 different vibrant areas! Fight enemies and find items around the map. Enjoy colorful and unique biomes, ranging from a beach to the snowy wilderness, and talk to NPCs to learn more about the story.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3131980/extras/38c6c52ec4eb1913e7e378ab7ff37e78.avif?t=1753943646\" width=616 height=215 /></span><br><br>Encounter unique enemies and bosses, and dodge bullet-hell style attacks in fun turn based battles! Discover the local enemies of each area. Time your various attacks just right to score major damage! (or, you know, awfully miss) Attack with a riskier but more rewarding beam cannon, or your own weapon.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3131980/extras/7e45ec3695861ed6c0f72d97b7a22b23.avif?t=1753943646\" width=616 height=214 /></span><br><br>Journey to destroy the evil King Spot and stop him from annihilating you, your friends, family, and your entire species! You might want to bring a blue friend with you too!",
